@DATABASE "Andy Capp"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - A - Andy Capp"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - A
                   ====================================

                                 Andy Capp
                                 =========


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====
            
@{"Infinite Kisses" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(43584,0)"}         43584,0
@{"Kisses = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(65099,255)"}         65099,x (x= 1-255)

                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
